  "confidenceNotes": "GOOD CONFIDENCE: eskwela (school — Spanish loanword escuela, widely attested across Philippine languages including Kapampangan), estudyante (student — Spanish loanword estudiante, widely attested), lapis (pencil — Spanish loanword lápiz, attested in Wiktionary Kapampangan section), klase (class/classroom — Spanish loanword clase, widely used), leksyon (lesson — Spanish loanword lección, widely used across Philippine languages), kaklase (classmate — ka- prefix + klase, standard Philippine derivational morphology attested in Tagalog and shared with Kapampangan)."
